title: *PATREON PREVIEW* The Afters with Très Bien’s Simon Hogeman
description:
On our new weekly lightning round mini ep with Très Bien’s Simon Hogeman, we’re fucking around with his brother Hannes, End Clothing, Inter Milan, bringing back brands from the dead, best-dressed cities, worst-dressed cities, sneaker sexual attraction, stylish subcultures, designer, streetwear and much more.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
